YOU ARE LIKE A WAVE IN THE OCEAN 🌊 

You are like a wave, you flow with a graceful rhythm, navigating life’s twists and turns with fluidity and resilience. Your energy surges and recedes, mirroring the ebb and flow of the tides, but your essence remains constant, a force of nature that adapts and perseveres. Like a wave, you carry the stories of the places you’ve been and leave your mark on the shores of memory, a reminder of the beauty in embracing life’s ever-changing currents. 

Concept and Direction- Diya Lulla
